                            },
                            {
                                "type": "link",
                                "name": "basic",
                                "alt": "basic",
                                "game-obj": "Rules",
                                "aonid": 2297
                            }
                        ],
                        "text": "With raucous shrieks, the shrieker crew charges forward. The troop Strides twice. If they move at least 10 feet, the crew deals 3d6+13 slashing damage (DC 23 basic   Reflex save) to each enemy in a 5-foot emanation at the end of the crew's movement. Each target who fails this save is also deafened for 1 round."
                    }
                },
